              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "64 events of the N-14(n,3a)T reaction were found"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The possible decay modes of this reaction are",
                "   successively (1.) via C-12 and Be-8",
                "             or (2.) via B-11 and Be-8",
                "             or (3.) via B-11 and Li-7",
                "   or (4.) Breakup into Be-8 and Li-7 and further",
                "           decay into 2alpha and T+alpha, respectively.",
                "It was found that process (1.) is highly predominant",
                "by at least 80%."
              ]
            }
          ],
